Requirements to run:
1) Use the 'debug_poisson' branch of underworld3, install with `pip install -e .`
2) Run the 'debug' branch of petsc4py at underworldcode, install with `pip install .` (no '-e')

Then execute:
  mpirun -np 4 python pure_py_ss.py ; /usr/local/lib/petsc/bin/petsc_gen_xdmf.py sol.h5
